Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特一大早就這麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這早餐看起來很美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加內特  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  你怎麼自己跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口  都怪你們完全不召喚我  閒得發慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  總找不到機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有點能讓我熱血沸騰的冒險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜  今天沒有任務委託吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近總是些要出遠門的任務  偶爾休息一天也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  Oasis工會今天放假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天也沒事幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放假啊  那爸爸今天能跟我一起玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來了一件修理道具的工作  一整天都得泡在工房里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那卡莉娜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有公務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按慣例得到中央廣場耍雜技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那切露西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露西今天有神殿騎士團的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有任務委託  大家還是很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這時代的人總是那麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提  尼克到附近的武器店整修斧頭去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  對不起了米內特  今天就跟加內特玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  和加內特一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:04:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  米內特  一會請你幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫什麼忙啊  尼娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都那麼忙  只能拜託米內特了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡蘿蔔  洋蔥  馬鈴薯…這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚飯用的咖哩的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有些事不能脫身  希望米內特能幫我去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這算是任務委託嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  這個任務我想委託給米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙買東西嗎？真能幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我會做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子人氣真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特現在在中高年齡層中大爆人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了「想讓她當女兒」NO.1  還建立了FANS團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有這麼高支持率？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你都是會員嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從尼娜小姐那接到的委託是  暗中看好米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟丟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也戴上這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  莉特絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我戴老花眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎歡迎  這不是米內特嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我想買蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡蘿蔔  洋蔥  還有馬鈴薯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬鈴薯賣光了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始就出意外了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  不過中央廣場那邊的店應該會有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就到那去買
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我給你們畫個地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  來  這個就算給你們當補償
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  第一關卡通過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過路線跟預定的不一樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央廣場那邊啊  挺遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特走向廣場的反方向了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該往這邊走的  她卻走反了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  得趕緊告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們的任務是暗中監視
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接跟她交談就違反規則了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  得在暗中偷偷看著他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從蔬菜店到中央廣場是走…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這音樂是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿尼艾絲的街上雜技
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？喂阿尼艾絲  那不是米內特和加內特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  買東西做得挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央廣場是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:08:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}我們正想到中央廣場  阿尼艾絲的雜技音樂就給我們帶路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這麼大的廣場  一般不會走錯的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然  又不是切露西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  比起這些我們不如快點到下個店舖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方真的會有蔬菜店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這里幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟切露約好了在這里見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆怎麼會到這里來？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近應該有蔬菜店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜店嗎？蒙緹你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近沒有目標店舖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了  確實在這附近有個新搬來的蔬菜店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報疏漏  那個店還沒有保存到資料中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是剛搬過來的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是卡莉娜  這個城的事你全都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里  店子就在那條街的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人能去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  這是我接受的委託  我要自己完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還  還有我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過切露西還真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  第二關卡突破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還擔心出什麼變數呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下一步去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在那幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是神聖的大教堂前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我們並不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這花眼鏡算什麼？瞧不起人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妹妹…喂  莉特絲也幫忙解釋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不在了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們一起過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊  聽我解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里真簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…只剩肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  馬上完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也都是多虧了我在你身邊  要感謝我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼在這里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在大教堂有騎士團的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大教堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  大教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是港口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這次不迷路我都很認真準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你這地步也算是一種才能了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  加內特  帶切露西到大教堂去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是任務還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下買肉了  我自己沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  米內特…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  切露西就由我負責帶她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加內特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受米內特的好意吧  切露西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  我知道了  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就交給你了  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是倒大霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀姐姐  你真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  為什麼你丟下我跑掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧姐姐  突然形勢大變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個神殿騎士  一直不相信我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「戴那種眼鏡的人說話怎麼能相信」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一一個夥伴加內特離開戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被孤立的米內特將要如何脫離這個危機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是華麗地無視我嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡蘿蔔  洋蔥  馬鈴薯  調味料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉店就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼地方痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是有點頭暈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係  經常這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你好痛苦的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下就會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個放到額頭上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好清涼好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明明沒閒工夫在路上耽誤時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姐姐是想說不管那個難受的女孩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是姐姐  對於對手  還是要盡早斬草除根
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壞我風評  不是啦  只是…只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去告訴米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  米內特是工會所屬的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  我也是冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕你  我身體不好所以不能到太遠的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:15:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話下次給我慢慢講述冒險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  你還在買東西的路上是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  最後只剩下肉店了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這種時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就跟我一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這里走就是近道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道得真詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的貓整天會到這里來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以連我都熟悉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆的家還養著貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像它當了這附近的貓老大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是有很多貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  那里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是下不來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像從那可以爬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能對小貓見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊來  來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝  這點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  下面…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上給你弄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道該怎麼謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要謝就謝這孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝小妹妹救了我家小玉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會報答你的  那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  為什麼爸爸會在那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧路過而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  只是覺得雷斯塔先生跟我哥哥很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常溫柔的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次讓我見個面吧  和貓一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我家是在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天玩得非常開心  米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再聊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我們也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了買肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你們倆回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  唯有肉沒有買到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算任務失敗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有完成任務  不過米內特做了比任務更重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧  不用放肉也可以做咖哩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜咖哩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  我正在減肥  正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  這麼晚過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送貨來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特等肥牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央街道的肉店托我們送的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是給Oasis的米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:20:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說「謝謝你救了我家的貓」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那個貓是肉店的貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜  這種場合該怎麼算呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  當然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  恭喜你  任務完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露西  加內特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了  切露？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會議都沒來  騎士團的人很擔心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來話長了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這個時代的城鎮路線那麼複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你們倆也一起吃晚飯如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡咖哩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過姐姐  你沒忘記吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟Oasis工會是宿命之敵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你竟然接受敵人的恩惠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得有這樣教育過姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不記得給你教育過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最近氣氛有點鬆  不過我們是對手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我是很樂意接受邀請的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我忙嗎  米內特？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是做好吃的咖哩的任務啊  尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～晚會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很榮幸能收到邀請…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特和阿尼有其他的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了  回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還減輕了20%左右的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我  有他們跟我一起呢
